title: Stephen Moore, William Barr & Venezuela

description:
Guests include Hagar Chemali, CEO of Greenwich Media Strategies and former Treasury spokesperson for Terrorism and Financial Intelligence, and former Spokesperson for the U.S. Mission to the United Nations and Ambassador Samantha Power.
